    "text_1": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>To mark 20 years of premium golf fashion, TRENDYGOLF and J.Lindeberg are offering you the chance to win an unforgettable stay at one of the most iconic golf destinations in the world: Turnberry.</p><p>And it's all tied to two exclusive pieces that define modern golf style – the Lachlan II and Lincoln II polos, reissued to celebrate two decades of partnership between TRENDYGOLF and J.Lindeberg.</p><p></p><h2><strong>The Prize: Play Where Legends Walk</strong></h2><p>One lucky winner (from the <strong>UK or US</strong>) will win:</p><ul><li><strong>Two nights in the Turnberry Lighthouse Suite</strong> – sleeping up to four people<br/><br/></li><li>A <strong>4-ball round on the King Robert the Bruce Course<br/><br/></strong></li><li>A <strong>4-ball round on the legendary Ailsa Course</strong>, reopening this May after its full renovation<br/><br/></li><li><strong>Breakfast for all guests at the 1906 Restaurant</strong> in the main hotel<br/><br/></li></ul><p>That’s right – this is your chance to play the Ailsa Course <strong>before the rest of the world</strong>. It’s a rare tee time on one of the most celebrated links courses, and you’ll be among the very first to experience it post-renovation.</p><p>And you’ll be doing it in serious style.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
