    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "The Products That Get You There",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>To celebrate this milestone, we’ve reintroduced two of the most iconic polos in modern golf-wear:</p><h3><a href=\"https://trendygolf.com/products/x-trendygolf-lachlan-ii-polo-jl-navy-2025?_fid=737314871&_pos=2&_ss=c&variant=55051510120834\" title=\"https://trendygolf.com/products/x-trendygolf-lachlan-ii-polo-jl-navy-2025?_fid=737314871&_pos=2&_ss=c&variant=55051510120834\"><strong>Lachlan II Polo – 20th Anniversary Edition</strong></a></h3><p>A clean, crisp reinterpretation of a JL classic. With sharp cut lines, high-performance fabric, and that unmistakable J.Lindeberg edge, the <strong>Lachlan II</strong> brings effortless style and all-day comfort to the course and beyond.</p><h3><a href=\"https://trendygolf.com/products/x-trendygolf-lincoln-ii-polo-jl-navy-2025?_fid=737314871&_pos=1&_ss=c&variant=55051510284674\" title=\"https://trendygolf.com/products/x-trendygolf-lincoln-ii-polo-jl-navy-2025?_fid=737314871&_pos=1&_ss=c&variant=55051510284674\"><strong>Lincoln II Polo – 20th Anniversary Edition</strong></a></h3><p>The Lincoln II takes a bold stance, combining technical finesse with heritage-inspired detail. Finished with the signature JL bridge logo and modern tailoring, this is a must-have piece for those who demand precision in every detail.</p><p>These polos are <strong>exclusive to TRENDYGOLF</strong> and produced in limited quantities. Owning one means being part of the brand’s legacy – and it might just get you to Turnberry.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
