        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Simple. Stylish. No nonsense.</p><ul><li><strong>1 entry for every J.Lindeberg item purchased<br/><br/></strong></li><li><strong>2 entries for every TRENDYGOLF x J.Lindeberg Anniversary Polo (Lachlan II or Lincoln II)<br/><br/></strong></li></ul><p>Every item counts. The more you shop, the better your chances. Whether you’re upgrading your wardrobe or grabbing one of the anniversary pieces, your purchase puts you in the running.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
