        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Why This Trip Matters",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Turnberry’s Ailsa Course isn’t just another round – it’s history. It’s Open Championship moments. Its coastal drama and world-class layout are reimagined for a new era.</p><p>Staying in the <strong>Lighthouse Suite</strong>, perched right on the edge of the Atlantic, you’ll wake up to views that most golfers only dream of. And with access for up to four guests, it’s not just a solo trip – it’s a chance to bring your crew along for something unforgettable.</p><p>No travel is included, but the prize itself? Absolutely priceless.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
